Call ECR_TRACE(mess(406,184,1)-" : "-GSTK_CUNSSSNUM-","-GSTK_CUNLISNUM-","-[F:CUD2]ITMREF-","-[M:SNL1]LOT (nolign-1)-","-[M:SNL1]ECCVALMAJ (nolign-1),1) From GESECRAN
